      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>aubergine[s]</strong> into approx. 1cm rounds</p><p>Add the <strong>aubergine slices </strong>to a tray (or two!) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven and cook for 20 min or until cooked and tender</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1618924538070-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
