          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1618924667958-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>cornflour </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> in a small bowl, then beat in your<strong> egg[s]</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>,<strong> half</strong> of your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>white sauce</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't worry if it looks a bit grainy!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1618924690879-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
