          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1618924690879-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1618924690879-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1618924690879-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1618924690879-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> lentil filling</strong> has thickened, transfer it to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> roasted aubergine slices</strong></p><p>Dollop the <strong>white sauce</strong> all over, spreading it over the aubergine slices with the back of a spoon until evenly coated</p><p>Sprinkle over the<strong> remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until golden – this is your <strong>lighter aubergine & lentil moussaka</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1618924786698-x200.jpg",
