            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1618924786698-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the moussaka is cooking, chop your <strong>parsley</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Use the remaining time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
