    {
      "instruction": "<p>Leave the <strong>lighter aubergine & lentil moussaka</strong> to stand for a few min before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
